revisions.description: Added a OIDs for MACSEC on S-Series and 7100 series products.
Updated the CONTACT-INFO clause. Added OIDs for S1 User Capacity and SSA/Purview Appliance Flow Capacity.
Added an OID for 7100G Series Advanced Routing.
Updated the CONTACT-INFO clause. Added OIDs for K Series Chassis Virtual Switch Bonding and 7100K Series Advanced Routing.
Added an OID for the S Series S1 Chassis Virtual Switch Bonding.
Added OIDs for the S Series Multi-slot Virtual Switch Bonding and S Series Standalone Virtual Switch Bonding.
Added OIDs for the K Series per port user capacity license and S Series standalone user capacity license.
Added an OID for the K Series routing feature.
Added OIDs for the S Series licensable features.
Added an OID for the G Series Routing feature.
Added an OID for the D Series Policy feature.
Added an OID for the hardware based N-EOS-L3-DIAMOND license key.
Added an OID for the N-EOS-GPOLICY license key.
Added an OID for the C Series IPV6 Routing feature.
Added OIDs for the B Series Routing feature and the C Series Advanced Routing feature.
Added an OID for the B Series Policy feature.
Added an OID for the N-EOS-PPC license key.
The initial version of this MIB module.

etsysLicenseKeyOidsMIB.description: This MIB module defines a portion of the SNMP enterprise MIBs under Enterasys Networks' enterprise OID pertaining to OIDs for licensable features on Extreme Networks' devices. The OIDs contained in this module are intended to be returned by the etsysLicenseKeyIdentifier of the ENTERASYS-LICENSE-KEY-MIB.
